27
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:11,490
will be under your control.

28
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:12,480
Okay, Mother.

29
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:15,080
If I solve the crisis,

30
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:17,240
remember to give me the bracelet.

31
00:01:17,320 --> 00:01:19,320
