43
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:50,000
you have to put in your own money.

44
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,280
I don't want to pour my dowry down the drain.

45
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,400
So, this is

46
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:54,530
simply not worth it.

47
00:01:55,039 --> 00:01:56,200
So,

48
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,920
the Fourth Young Madam can't solve it, either?

49
