58
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:24,560
But the Fourth Young Madam has only been here for a month, and has already overthrown her.

59
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,160
She's indeed somebody.

60
00:02:27,920 --> 00:02:28,960
