61
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:33,520
Anyway, the household management power will be mine one day.

62
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:36,020
Let Liu Xizhao do whatever she wants for now.

63
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:50,640
