78
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:24,730
and try to sell it at the highest price.

79
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,579
But we lack resources.

80
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,840
We should solve this problem first.

81
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,760
The largest income

82
00:03:31,760 --> 00:03:34,560
for the Marquis's Mansion comes from these farms.

83
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,079
Look at this Xuanqing Farm.

84
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:37,280
It's the largest one,

85
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,360
but in recent years,

86
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:40,280
it has paid the least money.

87
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:44,160
Only 150 catties of grains for every mu of land.

88
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,720
It was more than 600 catties per mu five years ago.

89
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,780
The difference is more than a little.

90
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,300
