106
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,640
move back to live with Young Madam?

107
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:27,040
If there's nothing else,

108
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,330
go and air the books.

109
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:29,880
Yes.

110
00:04:37,240 --> 00:04:39,240
I heard you're temporarily in charge of managing the household.

111
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,480
If you need my help,

112
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:41,480
I can consider it.

113
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:41,960
No need.

114
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:43,800
I want to borrow Qingshan

115
00:04:43,960 --> 00:04:46,220
to accompany me in patrolling the farms.

116
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,960
The Eldest Sister has been grounded for three months.

117
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:50,320
No one will give you a hard time.

118
00:04:50,320 --> 00:04:52,320
You could have left this mess alone.

119
00:04:52,640 --> 00:04:56,170
You're not a person who covets the household management power.

120
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,320
You want Mother's bracelet.

121
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,560
What's so strange about that bracelet?

122
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,520
What can be so strange about a bracelet?

123
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:05,320
Of course I want the real power.

124
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:08,890
If I want to establish a foothold in this mansion,

125
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,000
of course I have to please the Old Madam.

126
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:11,760
Whether you can establish a foothold

127
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:13,080
is not clear yet.

128
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:15,600
The affairs of the Marquis's Mansion are intricate and entangled.

129
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,330
They are not that easy to solve.

130
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:19,120
I'll leave Qingshan to you.

131
00:05:19,120 --> 00:05:21,380
I'm going to the Imperial City Division.

