141
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,240
Zhang Da,

142
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,520
you trespassed on the haunted house.

143
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:52,600
Now you are crazy because of the scare.

144
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:54,000
You're lucky to be even alive.

145
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,760
Take him away.

146
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,640
Lock him up!

147
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:58,720
You two,

148
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,290
take those away.

149
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,920
You will be cursed!

150
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,480
Bailiff Wu.

151
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:10,280
This is the Fourth Young Madam from the Marquis of Changping's Mansion.

152
00:06:10,280 --> 00:06:14,340
She's here to patrol the farms on behalf of His Lordship and Her Ladyship.

153
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:18,640
So you're the Fourth Young Madam who's newly married.

154
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:20,100
At your wedding ceremony,

155
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:22,600
His Lordship treated me to a drink.

156
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,440
