157
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,200
you have to call me Uncle.

158
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:29,720
I'm a woman now.

159
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,860
I can't be looked down upon by him.

160
00:06:32,640 --> 00:06:33,400
Bailiff Wu,

161
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:36,240
Mother asked me to patrol the farmers for her.

162
00:06:37,520 --> 00:06:39,380
Let's get down to business first.

163
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,360
Okay.

164
00:06:42,760 --> 00:06:43,280
Please.

165
