195
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,240
We'd better wait for Bailiff Wu to come back.

196
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,400
You mean

197
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:03,160
Bailiff Wu is more authoritative than me?

198
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,680
No, no, no.

199
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,280
