210
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:28,560
Originally,

211
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:30,160
I wanted to choose carefully

212
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:32,480
before signing the contract with them.

213
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:36,320
It's just a formality, Bailiff Wu.

214
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,120
Don't think too much.

215
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:41,010
Take me out for a walk around

216
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,840
while the sun is still up.

217
00:08:44,520 --> 00:08:45,280
Young Madam,

218
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:47,160
it's raining outside.

219
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:49,480
Shall we take a rain check?

220
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,360
What?

221
00:08:50,560 --> 00:08:53,220
Bailiff Wu, do you have anything shady going on?

222
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,200
No, no, no.

223
00:08:55,560 --> 00:08:56,440
Young Madam,

224
00:08:57,560 --> 00:08:58,360
please.

225
00:08:58,880 --> 00:08:59,680
Please.

226
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:12,690
Young Madam.

227
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,440
This way.

228
